{"tid":21421,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"查實唔多公平","createTime":"2016-12-03T21:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T01:24:15.000Z","uid":27653,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a414084753e4f11ec4615cd455c5b58ab8729b6d","tid":21421,"uid":27653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T21:31:07.000Z","msg":"苦痛都係因人而異，所以究竟邊個先係最慘嘅，根本就冇辦法比較。<br />\n但如果將完全相同的苦痛施與兩個人。<br />\n忍耐力勁果邊可能唔會出聲，但弱果邊就會叫哂春咁。<br />\n<br />\n照道理，忍耐力勁果個人應該先係更加值得尊敬嘅。<br />\n但係呢個世界卻將叫春果班撚樣稱作「可憐的人」仲會溫柔咁對待佢地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而真係忍得果班就要自己頂哂，望住班撚樣搏同情。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90eff2c5d4646241914a7e800c93d3fec7d0ee71","tid":21421,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T21:33:12.000Z","msg":"公平與公義"},{"pid":"f6f8d0f06773f30a774c38b331e4411289928380","tid":21421,"uid":50298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T21:48:21.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"7626e20645777c670a3a1afac78c20481ecd7259","tid":21421,"uid":14832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T21:50:47.000Z","msg":"所以你見到叫春既都係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8752b675c0d9ae17cc27cb2b0a4e52721fcaab9d","tid":21421,"uid":40200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T22:03:36.000Z","msg":"忍耐是積極抵抗，示弱是消極抵抗"},{"pid":"03fc23af5cdf02d9332130b5efb51607a19819b6","tid":21421,"uid":27653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:23:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以你見到叫春既都係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同埋狗公"},{"pid":"d2f16db54c877292a93206ecc5c366c06141dcfe","tid":21421,"uid":27653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:25:21.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b77245e2c78efbe067f71a6676fd68a157bc8942","tid":21421,"uid":27653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"